  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nStar Atlas: Surge event rules!\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the Surge event.\nStar Atlas Surge Event 4/20 Part ONE\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about him playing Star Atlas Surge.\nSTAR ATLAS SURGE [LIVE]\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about him playing Star Atlas Surge.\nMetaverse Nomads #143 Surge and ONI Secures First Tier 2 Starbase w/ @DominicVain\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video of their weekly Star Atlas livestream.\nA Metaverse in Expansion — Star Atlas Acquires Assets and Intellectual Property from Multichain Ventures, including the Tokes brand, and Introduces In-game Cultivation\nStar Atlas published an article about their acquisition of Multichain Ventures.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #126\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nNoot ASMR lore keepers #1\nStar Atlas TV posted a video replay of the Star Atlas Lore Keepers.\nAtlas Brew #108\nStar Atlas TV posted a video reply of the latest Atlas Brew.\nMichael Wagner Addresses Star Atlas Community Blowback On Acquisition Of Multichain Ventures\nHologram News published an article about Michael Wagner addressing the acquisition of Multichain Ventures.\nSTARBASED – THE MISSING MANUAL!\nAephia updated their SAGE Starbased manual.\nStar Atlas: Cultivation Facilities w/ Tokes Token Integration\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about Star Atlas cultivation facilities.\nAtlas Brew #108: Community Updates & SURGE TLDR\nBeth posted a video recap of the latest Atlas Brew.\nSTAR ATLAS #230 DRAMA in STAR ATLAS – Commentary On Mikes Message & Tokes Acquisition\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about his thoughts on the Tokes acquisition.",
